  "title": "A yellow UFO spotted in Londrina-PR [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/18/a-yellow-ufo-spotted-in-londrina-pr-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-uT",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH, 6th, 1999</strong>. Time: 10h20 pm. Duration: 10 seconds. In Colina Verde, Londrina, State of Paraná, a person spotted an unidentified flying object heading West. According to the witness, the UFO was the size of an airplane and emitted a yellow light, flying at a slow speed. Despite the sighting taking place under clear skies and good visibility conditions, no traces of condensation were reported from the object, nor video records or photographs of the event that lasted ten seconds.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.541. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Londrina, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
